18. The Plaintiff claims interest on the suit amount as follows:
   (a) Pre-suit interest at the rate of {{INTEREST_RATE}}% per annum from {{TERMINATION_DATE}} till the filing of this suit;
   (b) Pendente lite interest at the rate of {{INTEREST_RATE}}% per annum during the pendency of this suit;
   (c) Future interest at the rate of {{INTEREST_RATE}}% per annum from the date of decree till actual realization.

filled_sections.prayer:
19. In the premises stated hereinabove, it is most respectfully prayed that this Hon'ble Court may be graciously pleased to:
   (a) Pass a decree in favour of the Plaintiff and against the Defendant for the sum of Rs. {{DAMAGES_AMOUNT}}/- (Rupees {{DAMAGES_WORDS}} Only) together with interest as claimed hereinabove;
   (b) Award pre-suit interest at the rate of {{INTEREST_RATE}}% per annum from {{TERMINATION_DATE}} till the date of filing;
   (c) Award pendente lite interest at such rate as this Hon'ble Court deems just and reasonable;
   (d) Award future interest from the date of decree till the date of actual realization;
   (e) Award costs of this suit including pre-litigation costs incurred for issuing legal notice;
   (f) Grant such other and further relief as this Hon'ble Court deems fit and proper in the facts and circumstances of the case.

